- @page_title = "Our partners - About"
= render 'about_nav'
%section.content
  .inner
    .main

      %h2 Our fantastic partners
      %p
        We just couldn't have developed Cunary without the help from the partners listed
        below. Go and check out their sites, if you work with Rails we're sure you'll love
        their work!
  
      %ul.partners
        %li
          %h3= link_to image_tag('partners/viaduct.svg', :width => 180), "http://viaduct.io"
          %p
            = link_to "Viaduct", "http://viaduct.io"
            provide an awesome hosting platform for Rails, Node.js & PHP applications.
        %li
          %h3= link_to image_tag('partners/atech.svg', :width => 200), "http://atechmedia.com"
          %p
            = link_to "aTech Media", "http://atechmedia.com"
            are a UK-based Rails development company specialising in working
            with techs.
  

        %li
          %h3= link_to image_tag('partners/codebase.svg', :width => 200), "http://www.codebasehq.com"
          %p
            = link_to "Codebase", "http://www.codebasehq.com"
            is a code hosting solution for software development teams.
        %li
          %h3= link_to image_tag('partners/deploy.svg', :width => 140), "http://www.deployhq.com"
          %p
            = link_to "Deploy", "http://www.deployhq.com"
            is a web-based deployment platform for Git & Subversion repos
            with FTP, SFTP & the cloud.

        %li
          %h3= link_to image_tag('partners/deliver.svg', :width => 120), "http://www.deliverhq.com"
          %p
            = link_to "Deliver", "http://www.deliverhq.com"
            offers a world-class e-mail delivery platform for sending & receiving messages.


